# API Rules

## Route Pattern
- Validate request body/query with Zod before any logic
- Use requireAuth middleware on all routes except /auth/*
- Use requireLicense on all report routes
- Always return { error: string } on errors with correct HTTP status
- Always return { data: ... } on success

## Supabase
- Use the service role client for all server-side DB operations
- Never use the anon client server-side
- Always check for Supabase errors before using the returned data

## Security
- Stripe webhook must verify signature before processing
- Rate limit: 200 req/15min global, 10 req/15min on auth routes
- Never log full request bodies (may contain tokens)
